    <item>
      <title>加拿大大使警告称，美国将采取“针锋相对”的报复措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/canadian-ambassador-warns-of-tit-for-tat-retaliation-to-us-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据加拿大驻华盛顿大使称，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税计划将引发加拿大“针锋相对”的报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/canadian-ambassador-warns-of-tit-for-tat-retaliation-to-us-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 23:43:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市新拥堵收费区交通量下降 7.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/nyc-s-new-congestion-pricing-zone-sees-7-5-drop-in-traffic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在纽约市实施交通拥堵收费计划的第一个工作周内，纽约市最繁忙街道的交通量下降了 7.5%，大多数通往曼哈顿的主要路口的早间通行时间也缩短了，这表明一些驾驶者改变了驾驶模式，以避开新的收费站。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/nyc-s-new-congestion-pricing-zone-sees-7-5-drop-in-traffic</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 23:03:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利推进补贴法案 避免掠夺可再生能源利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/chile-sidesteps-renewables-profit-grab-in-advancing-subsidy-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利众议院批准了一项扩大对低收入家庭电力补贴的法案，但删除了一项通过抑制可再生能源行业部分利润来筹集部分所需资金的措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/chile-sidesteps-renewables-profit-grab-in-advancing-subsidy-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 22:59:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德克萨斯州议员认为加州消防援助与政策变化有关</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/texas-lawmaker-sees-california-fire-aid-tied-to-policy-changes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着致命的山火继续在洛杉矶肆虐，来自德克萨斯州的一名共和党议员表示，联邦立法者将考虑将加州的救援资金与该州的政策变化挂钩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/texas-lawmaker-sees-california-fire-aid-tied-to-policy-changes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 22:20:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任期开始前，卢比奥担任国务卿的权威就已受到威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/marco-rubio-nomination-overshadowed-by-trump-s-special-envoy-picks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员马尔科·卢比奥是唐纳德·特朗普提名的国务卿人选，但在就职典礼前的几周里，这位当选总统的特使受到了最多的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/marco-rubio-nomination-overshadowed-by-trump-s-special-envoy-picks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 22:12:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队研究利用紧急权力逐步提高关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/trump-team-studies-gradual-tariff-hikes-under-emergency-powers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的新经济团队成员正在讨论逐月缓慢提高关税，这种渐进的方式旨在提高谈判筹码，同时有助于避免通胀飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/trump-team-studies-gradual-tariff-hikes-under-emergency-powers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:43:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
